            <div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">
                
                <p n="1"><supplied reason="lost">fourteenth</supplied> year of the king Parakesarivarman.</p>
                
                <p n="2-6">
                    In this year,
                    by order of Mayiṉmalai Irukkaivēḷāṟ,
                    we, the temple officers,
                    ...
                    <supplied reason="lost">this is the manner in which</supplied>
                    ...
                    made a donation.
                </p>
                
                <p n="6">
                    I, Mūvēntavēḷāṉ of Ollaiyūr,
                    by order of Mayiṉmalai Irukkaivēḷāṟ, 
                    I have given.
                </p>
                
                <p n="6"><supplied reason="subaudible">This is under the</supplied> <supplied reason="lost">protection</supplied> of the Paṉmāheśvarar-s.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The same individuals (Mayiṉmālai Irukkaivēḷār, Mūvēntavēḷāṉ of Ollaiyūrnāṭu) appear also in a similar transaction in <ref target="DHARMA_INSKotumpalur00031"/>.</p>
            </div>
            
